file: tmp_【#おかころ2周年3Dライブ】デビューして2年になりました。みんなにありがとう！【戌神ころね⧸猫又おかゆ】 [v8tFy6_6R84]_gemini-3-flash-preview/reencoded/part_006.mov

scenes.description: Korone and Okayu finish performing a song and transition into the MC segment.
The MC segment continues with 'Photo Time,' where the duo performs various poses for the audience to screenshot.

subtitles.original: ららららら～ 響け、あなたに！
subtitles.english: La la la la la~ reach you!

subtitles.original: 大好きだった
subtitles.english: I loved you.

subtitles.original: いぇーい！
subtitles.english: Yay!

subtitles.original: みんなの気持ちをね、こう、ね、代弁してね
subtitles.english: I'm speaking on behalf of everyone's feelings.

subtitles.original: かわいいよー！かわいいよー！
subtitles.english: You're so cute! You're so cute!

subtitles.original: 僕はね、あれだから。うん、うん。ころさんはやっぱ、うーんってなってた
subtitles.english: As for me... yeah. Korone-san was like, 'Mmm,' after all.

subtitles.original: 本当にありがとう！保護者だね、もう
subtitles.english: Thank you so much! You're like a guardian now.

subtitles.original: そう、もうね、うん、うん。さすがだね、分かってたけどね、みたいな
subtitles.english: Right, exactly. As expected, I knew it, though.

subtitles.original: ありがとね
subtitles.english: Thanks.

subtitles.original: で、こん、えっと、今の時間はね、えっと、
subtitles.english: So, now... well, at this time...

subtitles.original: このアイドル衣装でおかころってなかなかね、二人で配信することないから
subtitles.english: the two of us rarely stream together as OkaKoro in these idol outfits,

subtitles.original: 確かに
subtitles.english: True.

subtitles.original: 本当に。ちょっと待って
subtitles.english: Really. Wait a sec.

subtitles.original: 大丈夫？
subtitles.english: Are you okay?

subtitles.original: 今更ちょっと疲れがきた
subtitles.english: I'm starting to feel the fatigue now.

subtitles.original: 大丈夫だよ。じゃあ、僕が代わりに
subtitles.english: It's okay. I'll take over.

subtitles.original: この衣装で、まぁ、二人で並ぶ事ってすごい珍しいので、
subtitles.english: Since it's very rare for the two of us to stand side-by-side in these outfits,

subtitles.original: 今回は、えっと、少しの時間、おかころの写真撮影をしていこうかなと思います
subtitles.english: I think we'll do an OkaKoro photo shoot for a bit.

subtitles.original: いぇーい！やったー！
subtitles.english: Yay! Hurray!

subtitles.original: なんかね、コメントにね、どんなポーズが欲しいかとかね、色々ね
subtitles.english: Like, let us know in the comments what kind of poses you want.

subtitles.original: そうだね、教えてもらえれば... 教えてもらいつつ...
subtitles.english: Yeah, if you could tell us... while taking suggestions...

subtitles.original: そうだね、それにお答えしていこうかなって。フォトタイムということで
subtitles.english: Right, we'll try to do those. It's photo time.

subtitles.original: スクショタイムということで、みんなこの上のタグをさ、つけてさ、
subtitles.english: Since it's screenshot time, if everyone used the tag up there,

subtitles.original: あの投稿してくれたらすごい嬉しいよ
subtitles.english: and posted them, I'd be really happy.

subtitles.original: 嬉しいよ
subtitles.english: We'd be happy.

subtitles.original: ありがとう
subtitles.english: Thank you.

subtitles.original: あ、カメラある、カメラある
subtitles.english: Ah, there's a camera, there's a camera.

subtitles.original: わーわーわー
subtitles.english: Wah wah wah!

subtitles.original: いいね、いいね。どんなポーズがいいかな？
subtitles.english: Nice, nice. What kind of pose should we do?

subtitles.original: あ、ハートマーク作る？ハートマーク
subtitles.english: Oh, should we make a heart mark? A heart mark.

subtitles.original: そうだね、いいよ。じゃあ、手で作ろう、手で。よくいるやつ
subtitles.english: Right, okay. Let's make it with our hands. The usual one.

subtitles.original: いいよ
subtitles.english: Okay.

subtitles.original: ハートじゃない... あ、ごめんごめんごめん
subtitles.english: That's not a heart... Ah, sorry, sorry, sorry.

subtitles.original: ハート！
subtitles.english: Heart!

subtitles.original: ハートじゃない...
subtitles.english: That's not a heart...

subtitles.original: ごめんごめんごめん
subtitles.english: Sorry, sorry, sorry.

subtitles.original: うわぁー！
subtitles.english: Waaaah!

subtitles.original: うぇーい！ごめん、ごめんごめん
subtitles.english: Wheee! Sorry, sorry, sorry.

subtitles.original: もう。ごめん、すぐチューするんですけど
subtitles.english: Geez. Sorry, she keeps trying to kiss me.

subtitles.original: いいでしょ
subtitles.english: It's fine, right?

subtitles.original: 今日だけだから。ハート、これなら、大きいハートなら作れるんじゃない？
subtitles.english: Since it's only for today. Maybe we can make a big heart like this?

subtitles.original: 大きいハート。よし、いこう
subtitles.english: A big heart. Alright, let's go.

subtitles.original: どう？いいだろ
subtitles.english: How's this? Good, right?

subtitles.original: あ、待って、スクエアならいけるっしょ
subtitles.english: Oh, wait, we can do a square, right?

subtitles.original: あ、いけた、いけた。四角。四角
subtitles.english: Ah, we did it, we did it. A square. A square.

subtitles.original: これじゃダメかな？
subtitles.english: Is this no good?

subtitles.original: どうだろう。でも、みんな可愛いとは言ってくれてるけど
subtitles.english: I wonder. But everyone's saying it's cute.

subtitles.original: え、お尻も撮ってもらう？お尻も
subtitles.english: Should we let them take a photo of our butts? Butts too.

subtitles.original: お尻撮ってもらう。はいよー。しっぽ。アイドルしっぽです
subtitles.english: Let them take a photo of our butts. Okay. Tails. These are idol tails.

subtitles.original: あぁ、アイドルしっぽです
subtitles.english: Ah, these are idol tails.

subtitles.original: なんか、おかゆのしっぽと並ぶと本当にころねのしっぽさ、
subtitles.english: When lined up with Okayu's tail, doesn't Korone's tail look

subtitles.original: 立派じゃないかな？
subtitles.english: really magnificent?

subtitles.original: いや、それが可愛いんだよ。立派じゃん、立派
subtitles.english: No, that's what makes it cute. It's magnificent, magnificent.

subtitles.original: ありがとう。ちょっとやそっとのことじゃ千切れないからね
subtitles.english: Thank you. It won't tear easily, you know.

subtitles.original: 確かに僕のすぐ千切れちゃうからね
subtitles.english: True, mine tears easily.

subtitles.original: ちょっと分けてあげるから
subtitles.english: I'll give you a bit of mine.

subtitles.original: いらない。いらない
subtitles.english: I don't need it. I don't need it.

subtitles.original: 取れたかなみんな？取れた？
subtitles.english: Did you get it, everyone? Did you get it?

subtitles.original: やっぱ、僕たちはしっぽが可愛いからね、しっぽがね
subtitles.english: After all, our tails are cute, aren't they?

subtitles.original: そうだね。なんかコメントで、みんな良いよって言っていいんだよ、もっと
subtitles.english: Right. People in the comments, it's okay to say it's good, more.

subtitles.original: 自分をさらけ出して。どんな、どんなポーズがいいとか、本当にレアだからね
subtitles.english: Expose yourselves. Like what kind of pose you want... this is really rare.

subtitles.original: みんな分かってるこれ？
subtitles.english: Do you all understand that?

subtitles.original: いや、多分ね、ころね自身がね、おかゆとのね、あの、メモリーを残したいんだよ、きっと
subtitles.english: No, probably Korone herself wants to leave memories with Okayu, surely.

subtitles.original: そう、だからみんななんか。メモリーをね。そうだね。なんか
subtitles.english: So, everyone, please... Memories, yeah. Right. Something...

subtitles.original: 抱き合って、だって
subtitles.english: They said 'Hugging'.

subtitles.original: あー。抱き合ってる。そうだね。ぎゅー、ぎゅー。
subtitles.english: Ah, hugging. Right. Hug, hug.

subtitles.original: ぎゅーぎゅー
subtitles.english: Huggy huggy.

subtitles.original: 取れた？
subtitles.english: Did you get it?

subtitles.original: ハイタッチして、だって
subtitles.english: They said 'High touch'.

subtitles.original: いぇーい！
subtitles.english: Yay!

subtitles.original: あ、これ取れなくない？
subtitles.english: Ah, isn't this hard to capture?

subtitles.original: 確かに. みんなスローで、スローモーションで。スローモーションで
subtitles.english: True. Everyone, do it in slow motion. Slow motion.

subtitles.original: いぇーーい！
subtitles.english: Yaaaaay!

subtitles.original: 取れた？
subtitles.english: Did you get it?

subtitles.original: これなら。これなら取れるんじゃない？
subtitles.english: With this... with this, you can probably get it, right?

subtitles.original: 楽しいな
subtitles.english: This is fun.

subtitles.original: ね、すごい楽しい
subtitles.english: Yeah, it's really fun.

subtitles.original: ジャンプして、ジャンプして
subtitles.english: Jump, jump!

subtitles.original: わー。あ、一人で
subtitles.english: Wah! Ah, just one of us.

subtitles.original: 二人で。二人でジャンプする？
subtitles.english: Both together. Should we jump together?

subtitles.original: せーの、うぇーい！
subtitles.english: Ready, go! Wheee!

subtitles.original: でもなんかスカートめくれちゃうこれ
subtitles.english: But like, our skirts might flip up.

subtitles.original: あ、ダメだ、これダメだ。ダメだ。スカートめくれてしまうね
subtitles.english: Ah, no, this is bad. Our skirts will flip up.

subtitles.original: あと何だ？あ、あのさ、初めてのさ、おかころ3Dコラボ覚えてる？
subtitles.english: What else? Ah, you know, do you remember our very first OkaKoro 3D collab?

subtitles.original: フュージョンやったじゃん。あ、やった
subtitles.english: We did 'Fusion'. Ah, we did.

subtitles.original: やってもいいかな？
subtitles.english: Can we do it?

subtitles.original: フューー... ジョン！ハッ！
subtitles.english: Fu... sion! Ha!

subtitles.original: あー。あー。あー、失敗した
subtitles.english: Ah... ah... ah, we failed.

subtitles.original: 失敗したわ
subtitles.english: We failed.

subtitles.original: 失敗したわ。ダメだね
subtitles.english: We failed. No good.

subtitles.original: しばきあげパンチングだって。やってみて。カメラに近づいて
subtitles.english: They said 'Shibaki-age punching'. Try it. Get close to the camera.

subtitles.original: ほらよ！そんな感じなの？あ、どう、あ、普通にもっと
subtitles.english: Take that! Is it like that? Ah, how about... ah, just more normally...

subtitles.original: ほらよ！
subtitles.english: Take that!

subtitles.original: デンプシーロール
subtitles.english: Dempsey Roll!

subtitles.original: うぉー！うぉー！うぉー！
subtitles.english: Whoa! Whoa! Whoa!

subtitles.original: あ、観客も交えて撮影しない？
subtitles.english: Ah, should we take a photo with the audience too?

subtitles.original: あ、そうだね。オニキスとおにぎりゃー
subtitles.english: Ah, right. Onyx and Onigirya.

subtitles.original: こっち、こっち。よくさ、こうやって、こういうのやりたい、こういうの
subtitles.english: This way, this way. You know, I want to do this kind of thing.

subtitles.original: 確かに. すごい、いいじゃん！
subtitles.english: True. Wow, that's great!

subtitles.original: あ、いいじゃん！はぁー
subtitles.english: Ah, it's good! Haaah.

subtitles.original: いや、なんで最前取れなかったんマジで。カメラマン、カモンカモン
subtitles.english: Wait, why couldn't you guys take the front row, seriously? Cameraman, come on!

subtitles.original: カモンカモン。カモンカモン
subtitles.english: Come on, come on. Come on, come on.

subtitles.original: 最前入れよ
subtitles.english: Get to the front!

subtitles.original: 確かに. ギリギリ前取れてない感じだ
subtitles.english: True. Feels like we can't quite get to the very front.

subtitles.original: いぇーい。ピース、ピース。ピース。どう？取れたみんな？
subtitles.english: Yay. Peace, peace. Peace. How's that? Did you get it, everyone?

subtitles.original: いいじゃん。いいじゃん。ね、いいよね。はーい
subtitles.english: It's good. It's good. Yeah, it's nice. Okay.
